Ms. Hope S. TaitzELY AdvisorsNew York, NYShe founded Catalyst Partners, a money management firm. She began her career as a mergers and acquisitions analyst before becoming an associate at Drexel Burnham Lambert. Now acting as a consultant focused on analyzing and investing in retail/consumer industries, she is also a director of Apollo Residential Mortgage Inc. and several other financial services companies.2013 Third QuarterAdded to: Diamond Resorts International Inc. - Las Vegas, NVDiamond Resorts is a network of more than 300 vacation destinations in 33 countries. Revenues are $617 million.















 















 
























